Thanks for the advice. The truth is, 90% of the people out there using a Ghost Box are imitating Frank&#39;s Box, but are not using a Frank&#39;s Box. There are some variations. Since Frank Sumption only makes these boxes (on the instructions of &quot;spirits&quot;) for specific people, his supporters will always argue that we have to use it before debunking it. However, like 90% of the paranormal investigators using a version of a Ghost Box, we did do some tests. Sometimes we thought it worked but when held up against Cognitive Bias phenomenon, the results were not only inconclusive, but obvious we were getting caught up in trying to recognize only the words that made sense to the questions asked. 

But still, I truly appreciate your kind words and advice. To be honest, I&#39;m not looking for respect, just the truth. 

God bless.
